FF07 BUILDING USER FRIENDLY FORMS 2500
Where do you create a new form for an existing table?
     [   ] In the app’s home page 
     [   ] In the customize this form link 
     [ C ] In the table’s settings  
     [   ] In the reports & charts link 

Which are the versions of a form view?
     [ C ] Edit 
     [ C ] Add 
     [ C ] View 
     [   ] Delete 

When you set up a dynamic form rule, on what can you base your conditions?
     [   ] The table 
     [ C ] The field  
     [ C ] The user 
     [ C ] The record 



